name: Rapunzel's Tower
description: This is a set of three pixel pieces by Sebi: Sauron's Tower, Rapunzel's Tower, and Kong's Tower. The most iconic towers of all time in pop history. As a big believer in 1of1 NFTs, I want to contribute three towers to the Proto Towers collection. Here is the game:  Whoever holds all three for the first time will trigger an epic Tower OE, and oc will get number one airdropped as well as mentioned in the metadata!

attributes.value: In the tranquil sea behind Rapunzel's tower, verdant figures of friendly nature take joyous baths.
